        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.1rem);font-weight:900;color:#1A202C;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 16px;">Why Do You Need Marriage Certificate Attestation in the UAE?</h2>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;">Your marriage certificate is more than a personal document. In the UAE, it must be officially verified before government departments and many private organizations accept it. Completing the marriage certificate attestation process confirms that the document is genuine and legally recognized for use in the country.</p>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:24px;">You may need marriage attestation in the UAE for several important purposes.</p>
